The '''''Encyclopedia Galactica''''' was a reference book of some renown,<ref name="TRG1-93" /> published by [[TriPlanetary Press/Legends|TriPlanetary Press]] shortly before the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]]. The entry for [[Neimoidian/Legends|Neimoidians]] consisted of two words: ''See: [[Duros/Legends|Duros]]''. This was a point of contention for the Duros, most notably Duros [[Chief Representative Officer]] [[Hoolidan Keggle]].<ref name="HNN" />

